      "content": "it's hard to believe in \"healing\" when the person who made life worth living is gone. it feels so performative, like i'm just pretending to be a person. honestly, it feels like the only way to actually stop this pain is to just... stop. does that sound crazy? it feels like the only logical way to find any peace.",
